data.description: Look at this large 3/2 pool  home on an Acre, with a Pond, in Alva! This home features a screened in pool/patio area, with a view of the pond.  The home has a large extra room (3rd bed room) that can be a bedroom or den or living room, it features a separate door to the outside.  There is a long driveway, with the home sitting in the middle of the property.  It has an attached 2 car garage, as well as a small building in the rear.  The metal roof and accordion shutters were added in 2011.  The seller is offering an Elite Global Home Warranty, which is good for one year, with this purchase.  This home is just waiting for you to add your personal touch!  Schedule your private showing today!
